img: A waterfall flows up a mountainside.
Geysers shoot bright light into the sky at night.
Razorvine (see "Wilderness Hazards" in chapter 5, "Adventure Environments," of the Dungeon Master's Guide) grows in 10-foot-tall hedges shaped like animals.
